* Create Notebook\nTask from Scratch
** Steps
***_ Open Jobs & Pipelines
***_ Select Create → Job
***_ Enter descriptive task name
***_ Type: Notebook
***_ Source: Workspace
***_ Browse to notebook path
***_ Configure compute
***_ Create task
** Additional Tasks
***_ Add more notebook tasks
***_ Configure dependencies
***_ Build pipeline structure
** Auto-dependency
***_ Select existing task first
***_ New task inherits dependency
@endmindmap
